491f4f","tid":1906314,"uid":126164,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:36:52.000Z","msg":"如果話佢有影響迪基亞視線越位<br />\n個波一射佢就吹啦<br />\nVAR乜鬼野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"你呢句無敵<br />\n<br />\n如果要判十二碼<br />\n一開始就判啦 <br />\nVAR乜鬼野<br />\n<br />\n如果球波用手入<br />\n拍到手果下就吹啦<br />\nVAR乜鬼野<br />\n<br />\n一句格式否定晒VAR既存在<br />\n又可以引用落門線技術到<br />\n甚至網球既鷹眼<br />\n<br />\n如果拿度球波出界<br />\n一早Call Out啦<br />\n鷹眼乜鬼野"},{"pid":"de2845bb7c7874301635a7bdedaad7e3e5d7315a","tid":1906314,"uid":141176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"阿狗個球又計？"},{"pid":"f2d4bcc761b7f66f93904ecc924a9cb7ceae2638","tid":1906314,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20170811/57068825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170811%2F57068825&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=c205f15f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170811%2F57068825&h=3761805c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20170811/57068825</a><br />\n唔post英文驚班撚樣唔識睇<br />\n<br />\n另一個有關執法新例，就同越位有關；雖然上季已經立例講明，攻方球員處於越位位置，就算佢冇接觸到皮球，但如果有影響到守方，都算被視作越位，但上季球證冇一律嚴格執行，新一季就要求，所以球證都要嚴格執行，越位球員影響到防守球員就會被判罰越位；球場草地方面，英超就禁止再印上圖案或其他標誌。"},{"pid":"f73c349e5a470a06ae8a94bff94879684cc1c9e2","tid":1906314,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:46:09.000Z","msg":"認真，我都算反獌，但如果咁都計入<br />\n以後場場搵幾條友喺門前跳嚟跳去咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5837cdbe3e377517b4ece1666dc34e718db662","tid":1906314,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de2845bb7c7874301635a7bdedaad7e3e5d7315a","tid":1906314,"uid":141176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:12:11.000Z","msg":"阿狗個球又計？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"阿狗嗰球真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到依家都唔知點解會計，仲有手球<br />\n<br />\n只能講嗰陣雲加真係有D料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}